{"word":"ἀντίβιος","slug":"ἀντίβιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀντίβιος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:βία'><el>βία</el></a>\n<p/><i>opposing force to force</i>, <el>ἀντιβίοις ἐπέεσσι</el> with <i>wrangling</i> words, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>:—<a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> as <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> = <a href='S:ἀντιβίην'><el>ἀντιβίην</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/>"}]}